title: No Harrowing Icons?
body: I recently beat the teemoing more than a week ago and i dont have any of my new fancy icons. Will i get them or should i put in a ticket. i didnt beat the gauntlet just the normal teemoing, and i did gift something to someone

replies.body:
Those icons are being sent out until November 17th. If you don't have anything by then, please reach out in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any questions.
